sangeet samrat tansen ( king of music - tansen ) is a 1962 hindi biopic historical drama film directed by s. n. tripathi . produced by sur singar chitra it had lyrics by shailendra and swami haridas with music by s. n. tripathi . one of the popular songs from this film was " jhoomti chali hawaa " in raga sohni , sung by mukesh for bharat bhushan . the film starred bharat bhushan , anita guha , sabita chatterjee , david , sapru and mukri . the story is a biopic of the famous court singer musician , mian tansen , one of the navaratnas in emperor akbar â€™s court .